New and, IMHO, better version at Media:Cimiez-new.jpg.


Cimiez monastery in Nice, France.

I User:Ericd took this picture myself with a Zenit 11 and an Industar-50 50mm f/3.5 lens on Fuji Superia Reala 100.

Perspective was digitally corrected and the picture was tilted and cropped.

The picture was scanned from film.
